{"tid":1653695,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"騰訊恢復部分NBA直播 有網友指騰訊只暫時愛國一下","createTime":"2019-10-14T07:59:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T10:01:55.000Z","uid":130626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"aaffd7e22a099804a59b9bdbcf030535bd814387","tid":1653695,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"內地騰訊體育的NBA直播節目表，恢復部分比賽的直播，距離之前宣布抵制，只有約一個星期。<br />\n恢復直播的兩場季前熱身賽，分別是上季總冠軍速龍隊對公牛隊，及木狼隊對以色列球隊馬卡比。<br />\nNBA火箭隊總經理莫雷早前發表涉及香港的言論，騰訊體育上星期二下午宣布，暫停NBA在中國舉辦的季前熱身賽轉播安排。有網友指騰訊只是暫時「愛國一下」，風聲過了就繼續賺錢。有網友就說，騰訊上星期只是說停播NBA中國賽，沒有說要封殺NBA。<br />\n報道說，騰訊經過與阿里巴巴集團的激烈競爭，今年7月宣布取得2020至2025年的NBA中國數碼媒體轉播權，轉播費為15億美元的「天價」，是之前與NBA簽約合作5年的3倍價錢，刷新中國市場體育版權作價紀錄。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86nba%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E6%9C%89%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E6%8C%87%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E5%8F%AA%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%8B-073947703.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E6%2581%25A2%25E5%25BE%25A9%25E9%2583%25A8%25E5%2588%2586nba%25E7%259B%25B4%25E6%2592%25AD-%25E6%259C%2589%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E5%258F%258B%25E6%258C%2587%25E9%25A8%25B0%25E8%25A8%258A%25E5%258F%25AA%25E6%259A%25AB%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B-%25E4%25B8%258B-073947703.html&d=JMO6Z0a0EEbNsRtkVA0DAvuvrtn4HlyTxFQ%2BxjLCx7s%3D&h=1fbb94f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E6%81%A2%E5%BE%A9%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86nba%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E6%9C%89%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%8B%E6%8C%87%E9%A8%B0%E8%A8%8A%E5%8F%AA%E6%9A%AB%E6%99%82%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B-%E4%B8%8B-073947703.html</a><br />\n<br />\n好好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b168cc0b289a0a8682e6f1e8c6fbd49ee34daa43","tid":1653695,"uid":56453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0